<section id="skills" >
<h3> Skills & Expertise </h3>
 <p>
        Over the years, I have developed a diverse set of skills that allow me to create garments that are both beautiful and perfectly tailored. My skills extend beyond simply sewing clothes; they include design, fabric selection, craftsmanship, and client consultation.
    </p>

    <h3>1. Custom Garment Design</h3>
    <p>
        I excel at creating unique, custom-made designs that cater to the individual tastes and preferences of each client. From casual wear to formal attire, traditional clothing to contemporary fashion, I can translate ideas into wearable art.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>2. Precision Sewing & Tailoring</h3>
    <p>
        Precision is at the heart of everything I do. I take pride in perfectly measuring, cutting, and stitching each garment to ensure a flawless fit. Every seam, hem, and edge is executed with meticulous attention to detail.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>3. Alterations & Repairs</h3>
    <p>
        I provide professional alteration services to make sure your clothes fit perfectly. From resizing garments to adjusting hems, sleeves, and waistlines, I ensure every piece is comfortable and tailored specifically for the wearer.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>4. Fabric Knowledge & Selection</h3>
    <p>
        Choosing the right fabric is essential for creating garments that look and feel great. I have extensive knowledge of fabrics like cotton, silk, linen, denim, chiffon, and more, helping clients select materials that match their vision.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>5. Embroidery & Decorative Techniques</h3>
    <p>
        I specialize in adding beautiful decorative details to garments, including embroidery, appliqué, lacework, and other embellishments, creating one-of-a-kind pieces that truly stand out.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>6. Client Consultation & Personalized Service</h3>
    <p>
        I take the time to listen carefully to clients needs, providing guidance on design choices, colors, fabrics, and styles, ensuring the final garment aligns perfectly with their vision.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>7. Trend Awareness & Creative Innovation</h3>
    <p>
        I continuously explore fashion trends and new design ideas, blending traditional tailoring techniques with modern styles to create garments that are timeless yet contemporary.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>8. Time Management & Project Coordination</h3>
    <p>
        I carefully plan and organize my work, managing multiple garments and projects simultaneously, ensuring each client receives their orders promptly and professionally.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>9. Attention to Detail & Quality Control</h3>
    <p>
        From the first cut to the final stitch, I maintain high standards of quality in every garment I create, ensuring clothing that is durable, comfortable, and visually stunning.
    </p>
	<hr>
    <h3>10. Passion & Dedication</h3>
    <p>
        What truly sets me apart is my love for tailoring. Every garment I create reflects my dedication, creativity, and desire to make clients feel beautiful and confident.
    </p>
</section>
